Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來分房睡也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一出門我就睡不著
