Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼我能幫忙的嗎？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的蕃薯要削皮 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你很像啊
