;Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太陽下味道就隱藏起來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？ 
