Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是小孩子… 也能殺人

Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣有點涼了\N加上你又睡在窗邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些書… 你全都看完了嗎？ 
