;Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.17,0:24:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾松  暫時躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.79,0:24:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
