Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.09,0:25:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋村嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.44,0:25:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂先生！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.82,0:25:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你沒事！ 
